result.name: Yoshinoya

reviews.text: Traditional Japanese fast service restaurant. Noodles, rice, meat tasteful cooked. You can dine in or take away. I always take away and eat in my hotel room. They provide chop sticks and spoons, sauces and spices.
Good for value, stable quality no matter which location you go to
The prices low. Quite good.
I was disappointed at our meal here. Although the prices were low, the rice was too soggy, curry was below average, and the lemon ‘tea’ not what I expected.
For this price with quality, it is quite good.
